


MESSAGES(1L)      MISC. REFERENCE MANUAL PAGES       MESSAGES(1L)



NAME
     messages - quick count of messages in mailbox or folder

SYNOPSIS
     messages
     messages folder-name

DESCRIPTION
     _M_e_s_s_a_g_e_s counts the occurrences of "^From "  in  either  the
     current  incoming mailbox or the specified folder.  This is,
     in fact, a simple little shell script!!

